from solution import Solution

s = Solution()

tests = [
    (5, 7),
    (10, 15),
    (3, 3),
    (1, 1),
    (2, 3),
    (7, 7),
    (8, 15),
    (15, 15),
    (16, 31),
    (31, 31),
    (32, 63),
    (63, 63),
    (64, 127),
    (1000, 1023),
]

results = []
all_ok = True
for n, expected in tests:
    out = s.smallestNumber(n)
    ok = out == expected
    results.append((n, expected, out, ok))
    if not ok:
        all_ok = False

all_ok, results[:10]
